snippet.title: EVE Online | Pulse – New Dawn, Mining & Industry Updates
snippet.description:
Welcome to another new look EVE Pulse from inside Jita 4-4! Start playing EVE for free at https://eve.online/youtube_pulse191121 

This week's episode contains details on the following:   
[0:25] New Dawn   
[0:47] Mining waste & resources  
[1:16] Haulers 
[1:30] Industrial cores  
[2:00] Mining & industrial ship balancing 
[2:39] New exploration sites  
[3:14] Audio update – ship sounds  
[4:24] EVE Universe  
[4:42] Alliance Tournament XVII winners 
[5:10] Monthly Economic Report 
[5:36] Black Friday offers 

New Dawn - https://www.eveonline.com/news/view/new-dawn-new-quadrant 
Mining & industry changes UPDATE! – https://forums.eveonline.com/t/from-extraction-to-production-update/337887
New exploration sites - https://www.eveonline.com/news/view/new-dawn-new-quadrant 
Audio update - https://www.eveonline.com/news/view/patch-notes-version-19-10#Audio 
EVE Universe - https://universe.eveonline.com/ 
Community Beat - https://www.eveonline.com/news/view/community-beat-for-19-november 
Monthly Economic Report - https://www.eveonline.com/news/view/monthly-economic-report-october-2021
